data.name: NumberOfFilesAssociated
data.comment: Number of files 'associated' (found in the drop remote store, so didn't need to be uploaded to drop)

data.name: NumberOfFilesUploaded
data.comment: Number of files 'uploaded' (were not already found in the drop remote store)

data.name: TotalAssociateTimeMs
data.comment: Total time taken to complete all 'Associate' calls to ArtifactServices drop

data.name: TotalUploadTimeMs
data.comment: Total time taken to complete all 'UploadAndAssociate' calls to ArtifactServices drop

data.name: TotalUploadSizeMb
data.comment: Total size of all uploaded files in megabytes (note that this is not the same as the size of the drop, since it doesn't include files that were only associated).

data.name: TotalComputeFileBlobDescriptorForAssociateMs
data.comment: Total time taken to compute FileBlobDescriptors for 'Associate' calls

data.name: TotalComputeFileBlobDescriptorForUploadMs
data.comment: Total time taken to compute FileBlobDescriptors for 'UploadAndAssociate' calls
